  "title": "BAKERY MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Assist the bakery team in the preparation of pastry</li><li>Executive and maintain consistent recipes and presentation</li><li>Follow proper handling and right temperature of food products</li><li>Handle equipment in a safe and proper manner</li><li>Maintain workstations are clean and tidy with proper hygiene</li><li>Minimize the wastage and spoilage of ingredients</li><li>Ensure proper hygiene practices in accordance with food & beverage safety and hygiene standards</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of relevant experience</li><li>No experience applicants are welcome to apply</li><li>Willing to learn and have a strong passion for baking</li><li>Able to work independently with minimum supervision</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li><li>A valid food hygiene certificate will be an advantage</li></ul>",
